Summary: Stopped at a red light i noticed a series of flashing lights in the distance
divs: Sighting DetailsAt first i thought i was looking at a radio tower as the object grew closer i ruled this out,the closer the object came i was more curious as i have never seen anything like this before in the sky the light patterns and color were also unfamilar to me, the object had all red lights which would flash 1-2-1-2 and all five would light up at once. The object from the sort of looked like a cross as i passed the object the side view looked different then from observing it head on viewing the pictures it appeared to have a different shape upon driving passed the object. Overall i would say the event made me feel nervous.
